approaches to its conservation. Choice B is incorrect because the text doesn’t suggest that climatic changes in Sonora
would reduce competition for M. boolii or that conservation efforts are focused on understanding this specific dynamic. In
fact, the text implies that an ecosystem-based approach would consider climate among many other factors but doesn’t
specify how climatic changes might affect competition between species. Choice C is incorrect because the text doesn’t
suggest that the single-species approach would shift the focus of conservation efforts away from M. boolii itself—rather, it
