    '{"type":"multiple_choice","choices":{"A":"“The opportunities and advantages already offered and constantly increasing are greater than would at first be","B":"“The social and the picturesque charm of the long journey is singularly enhanced by the leisurely stops made for","C":"“The real journey begins, of course, at Chicago, and as these trains leave in the evening the traveller fares forth in the","D":"“One experiences a certain sense of detachment from ordinary day and daylight duties that is exhilarating.”"}}',
