compensated when their agricultural resources and knowledge are used by corporations. The text then states that the
protocol allows corporations to keep their agreements with Indigenous communities confidential, about which some
Indigenous advocates express concern. Choice C, when inserted into the blank, gives a good justification for the advocates’
