northern part of the state. The student wants to compare the total area covered by Taos Pueblo with the total areas of
various other Pueblo nations in the state. Looking at the table, the student finds that the total area of Taos Pueblo is 156.2
square miles, while the total area of Nambé Pueblo is ______
Which choice most effectively uses data from the table to complete the comparison?
A. 47.3 square miles.
B. 77.1 square miles.
C. 32.4 square miles.
D. 595.7 square miles.',
